<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>诗歌 on 亦青小站</title><link>https://chrisveon.github.io/tags/%E8%AF%97%E6%AD%8C/</link><description>Recent content in 诗歌 on 亦青小站</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Sep 2016 10:30:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://chrisveon.github.io/tags/%E8%AF%97%E6%AD%8C/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>读书郎</title><link>https://chrisveon.github.io/post/the-bookish-youth.html</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Sep 2016 10:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://chrisveon.github.io/post/the-bookish-youth.html</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;夜影落寒窗，持卷入梦床。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;经年风雨雪，烛下捧茶凉。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;刺骨悬梁瘦，书生昼夜忙。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;图谋功与利，遥盼状元郎。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;（五律仄起入韵）&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>浣溪沙·雨夜有感</title><link>https://chrisveon.github.io/post/riverside-sand-reflections-on-a-rainy-night.html</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Sep 2016 10:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://chrisveon.github.io/post/riverside-sand-reflections-on-a-rainy-night.html</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;夜雨淋湿鹦鹉枝，梧桐灯下子规啼，红消香断小荷池。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;翠幕摇风纱帐冷，朱檐水漏墨痕稀，此时难奈是相思。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>满江红·流火将消</title><link>https://chrisveon.github.io/post/the-river-runs-red-as-the-fire-star-fades.html</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Sep 2016 10:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://chrisveon.github.io/post/the-river-runs-red-as-the-fire-star-fades.html</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;流火将消，天边眺、海霞初见。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;回首望，旦暝几度，渐行渐远。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;易逝韶华何必论，来年夏至凌绝顶。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;逐浪儿，今放手一搏，无牵念。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;万里路，千里卷，&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;年少梦，谁能灭！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;定长驱策马，乘风跋浪。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>